Laravel Task Document
��Project Overview
Develop a Laravel-based application with Admin and User roles, including 
authentication, product management, order processing, and approval workflows.
��Authentication Module
Common Login System
• Single Login Page for both Admin & User
• Dropdown selection:
o Admin
o User
• Based on selection:
o Validate credentials
o Redirect to respective dashboard
Customer Login Features
• Email + Password + OTP (via email)
• OTP validity: 1 minute
• Use Mailtrap for email testing
��User Module
Public Access (Before Login)
• View:
o Products (Category-wise listing)
• Restriction:
o Cannot place orders without login
User Registration
• Fields:
o Name
o Email
o Mobile
o Password
• After registration:
o User goes to Admin Approval (Unverified Users)
User Login
• Only Admin Approved Users can login
• OTP verification required
User Dashboard
Header
• Logo (Left)
• Profile Name + Logout (Right)
User Features
1. My Profile
• Update:
o Profile Picture
o Name
o Mobile
2. Change Password
• Fields:
o Current Password
o New Password
o Confirm Password
3. Forgot Password ( Next Sprint )
• Email-based OTP verification
• Reset password flow
Address Management (Checkout)
First-Time User
• Enter:
o Name
o Email
o Mobile
o Address1, Address2
o City, State, Country, Pincode
Existing User
• Show saved addresses (Radio button selection)
• Option to:
o Select existing
o Add new address
Order Flow
Add to Cart → Checkout
• Only logged-in users allowed
Place Order
• On order creation:
o Reduce:
▪ Stock
▪ Saleable Quantity
• Show the selected product in right side section, left side Address related 
information need to show here
My Orders
• Show logged-in user’s orders
